    Scope and Contents
Record Series consists of Emplyee Information Bulletins, CIPCO monthly news magazines, Customer and Rate Data, and Annual Reports of the company. This collection was a gift to the UIS archives from former Sangamon State University Archivist Dean Debolt.  
